    <item>
      <title>五角大楼部署移动旅以确保与墨西哥的边界</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/pentagon-to-deploy-mobile-brigade-to-secure-border-with-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部长皮特·赫格斯（Pete Hegseth）正在派遣机械化的步兵和空中支援，以帮助确保美国与墨西哥边境，从而加强军队在移民执法中的作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/pentagon-to-deploy-mobile-brigade-to-secure-border-with-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 21:31:07 GMT</pubDate>
