    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙总理说，应避免政治危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/portugal-prime-minister-says-political-crisis-should-be-avoided</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙总理路易斯·黑山（Luis Montenegro）表示，该国应避免政治危机，因为他试图结束人们对与家族企业有关的潜在利益冲突的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/portugal-prime-minister-says-political-crisis-should-be-avoided</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 20:50:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列“准备”捍卫大马士革附近的叙利亚德鲁兹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/israel-poised-to-defend-druze-near-damascus-from-regime-forces</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防部长说，大马士革南部的城镇贾拉马纳（Jaramana）的少数民族德鲁兹（Druze）受到新叙利亚政权的攻击，他命令以色列部队有望在必要时帮助保护他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/israel-poised-to-defend-druze-near-damascus-from-regime-forces</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 18:24:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉海军接近圭亚那海岸附近的埃克森美孚船只</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/venezuelan-navy-approaches-exxonmobil-vessel-off-guyana-coast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据圭亚那国防军的说法，委内瑞拉巡逻船于周六进入圭亚那的水域，并将自己定位在埃克森美孚公司（Exxon Mobil Corp.）签约的一艘船只附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/venezuelan-navy-approaches-exxonmobil-vessel-off-guyana-coast</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 16:11:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其在伊斯兰圣月召唤科克萨尔高管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/turkey-probes-zorlu-holding-ceo-over-islamic-holy-month-email</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国营经营的Anadolu机构称，土耳其检察官召集商人Bekir Cem Koksal作证，作为一封有关一封电子邮件调查的一部分，该电子邮件警告Zorlu持有工人不要庆祝斋月的伊斯兰圣月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/turkey-probes-zorlu-holding-ceo-over-islamic-holy-month-email</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 15:39:28 GMT</pubDate>
